text: Tanja Szewczenko is a German figure skater. She got a bronze medal at the 1994 World Figure Skating Championships. Early life: She was born in 1977 to Vera Küke. Küke was part of the German ethnic group in Ukraine (then part of the Soviet Union). Szewczenko's (Ukrainian) father left the family when she was two years old. ==Related pages== *People in Germany with Ukrainian ancestry ==Sources== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:German figure skaters
